T1  - IT'S ABOUT TIME: IMPLICATIONS OF THE PERIOD LENGTH IN AN EQUILIBRIUM SEARCH MODEL
AU  - Wolthoff, Ronald
Y1  - 2014/08/01
PY  - 2014
DA  - 2014/08/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12073
T2  - International Economic Review
